Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Sakata Rice Crackers Wholegrain Original' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Sakata Wholegrain Rice Crackers Original is made with 2 seeds: linseeds and chia seeds. They're also gluten-free.

Sakata Wholegrain Rice Crackers are versatile and delicious. With a dip, topped with cheese or just on their own straight from the packet, Sakata Wholegrain Rice Crackers are the perfect snack the whole family can enjoy. The history of Sakata can be traced back to the Japanese village of the same name where Sakata's original "usuyaki" crispy rice cracker was first created. At the centre of Japanese cuisine is the art of simplicity -- a few ingredients skilfully combined to achieve a simple, unpretentious result. At Sakata we will always start with the highest quality ingredients, artfully crafting them into delicious rice snacks we hope you will love.
  • Gluten-free
  • Made with 2 seeds

Products.RichDescription:
Sakata Seaweed Rice Crackers are oven-baked, gluten-free and contain only natural colours & flavours. They're the perfect snack companion.

Sakata Seaweed Rice Crackers are versatile and delicious.
With a dip, topped with cheese or just on their own straight from the packet, Sakata Seaweed Rice Crackers are the perfect snack the whole family can enjoy. The history of Sakata can be traced back to the Japanese village of the same name where Sakata's original "usuyaki" crispy rice cracker was first created.

At the centre of Japanese cuisine is the art of simplicity -- a few ingredients skilfully combined to achieve a simple, unpretentious result. At Sakata we will always start with the highest quality ingredients, artfully crafting them into delicious rice snacks we hope you will love. 
  • Gluten-free
  • Oven baked
  • Natural colours & flavours

Products.RichDescription:
Smith's Thinly Cut Potato Chips deliver the same quality and our great taste you get from Smith’s Crinkle, but in a thinner, crispy chip with a lighter bite.


Smith's Thinly Cut Original Potato Chips are made with top quality Aussie potatoes and are simply peeled, sliced thinly & cooked to perfection for a light, crispy texture then sprinkled with our famous seasoning, so you can enjoy melt in the mouth chips with that unbeatable Smith's taste.




Smith's Thinly Cut Original Potato Chips:


  • Perfect size for the whole family or a party.

  • So stop reading, crack it open and start sharing.

  • Made from top quality Aussie potatoes.

  • Contains no artificial colours, no artificial flavours and are gluten free.



The original and the best!


Perfect for any occasion


Thinly Cut
